#note very interesting that KAT and KART sim even. Normally the R bumps IST up by a good 5-6 points, but my thought is that IRST is weaker when there are no vowels to play through. To demonstrate this, I simmed xAKT versus xAKRT, and in that case keeping IRST sims 4 points better. Another likely factor is that KART sets up a nice hook onto the pointier column K.
